data.description: Welcome to your private Cobb County retreat.  Almost 2 acres with a horse barn (with attached fencing) and stall, a 1,200 square foot (40 x 30) shop with power,  large format rolling doors, heavy duty metal shelving, a 60 gallon air compressor, and a large wood burning stove!  The home is a nearly stepless ranch featuring hardwood floors throughout most of the home.  A large living room leads to an updated kitchen complete with granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances that will remain with home, and all new rustic light fixtures throughout.  Bedrooms are very spacious with walk-in closets.  Master bedroom features 2 separate closets, with one having custom shelving  built-in.  There is also a 10 x 16 covered entertainment area that also features a hand built brick firepit/grill!  The oversized back deck is nearly new and the back yard also features a 40 x 30 dog kennel or chicken run complete with chicken house.  The home also has a security system that consists of 6 hardwired cameras that will be remaining with the property.  There is also an electronic gate at the driveway so you can keep out any unwanted visitors!  This is the best of country living in the city.  Nearly impossible to find in Cobb County and ready for you to put your spin on this rustic retreat.
